#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&artikulate; is a pronunciation trainer for improving and perfecting "
"pronunciation skills for a non-native language. For this, &artikulate; "
"provides courses created by native speakers, who recorded their own voices "
"as comparison material. A student can download these recordings in form of "
"courses from the Internet. The training then consists of iterative playing "
"of a native speaker's recording of some phrase, recording the own voice, and "
"comparing both until the result is good enough to proceed with the next "
"phrase."
msgstr ""
"&artikulate; je vaditelj izgovorjave za izboljšanje in izpopolnjevanje "
"sposobnosti izgovorjave za tuje jezike. Za to &artikulate; nudi tečaje, ki "
"so jih ustvarili naravni govorci, ki so posneli lastne glasove kot "
"primerjalni material. Študent si lahko te posnetke v obliki tečajev prenese "
"z interneta. Usposabljanje je nato sestavljeno iz iterativnega predvajanja "
"posnetka neke fraze maternega govorca, snemanja lastnega glasu in primerjave "
"obeh, dokler rezultat ni dovolj dober za nadaljevanje z naslednjo frazo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Learning Concept"
msgstr "Koncept učenja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The study concept of &artikulate; is based on honest self-assessment of the "
"student. A student trains several phrases in one training session. For each "
"such phase, first he/she plays the native speaker recording for the phrase "
"and listens to it. Then, by recording his/her own voice when attempting to "
"repeat this phrase, we get a second recording. The student then can compare "
"both recordings and either decides that the phrase is mastered or that "
"another attempt is needed. The provided courses provide trainings for "
"special scenarios (like ordering food in a restaurant) but can also focus on "
"learning how to pronounce difficult syllables and words of a particular "
"language correctly."
msgstr ""
"Študijski koncept &artikulate; temelji na pošteni samooceni študenta. "
"Študent trenira več besednih zvez v enem treningu. Za vsako takšno fazo "
"najprej predvaja posnetek maternega govorca za frazo in ga posluša. Nato s "
"snemanjem lastnega glasu, ko poskuša ponoviti to frazo, dobimo drugi "
"posnetek. Študent lahko nato primerja oba posnetka in se bodisi odloči, da "
"je besedno zvezo obvladal ali da je potreben še en poskus. Zagotovljeni "
"tečaji nudijo usposabljanje za posebne scenarije (na primer naročanje hrane "
"v restavraciji), lahko pa se osredotočijo tudi na učenje pravilne "
"izgovorjave težkih zlogov in besed določenega jezika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "First Steps in &artikulate;"
msgstr "Prvi koraki v &artikulate;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "This chapter explains how to make the first steps in &artikulate;."
msgstr "To poglavje pojasnjuje, kako narediti prve korake v &artikulate;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "1. Download a New Course"
msgstr "1. Prenesite nov tečaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can download courses through <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Download Courses</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. If the menubar is "
"not activated, you can open the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu></"
"menuchoice> menu by clicking at the top-right button. A download window will "
"appear, listing the available languages provided by the &kde; Community. You "
"can sort through them using the order by functions at the right. We download "
"the Polish course by clicking on <guilabel>Install</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Tečaje lahko prenesete prek <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Prenos tečajev</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če menijska vrstica "
"ni aktivirana, lahko odprete meni <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu></"
"menuchoice> s klikom na zgornji desni gumb. Pojavilo se bo okno za prenos s "
"seznamom razpoložljivih jezikov, ki jih ponuja Skupnost &kde;. Razvrstite "
"jih lahko po vrstnem redu po funkcijah na desni. Tečaj poljščine prenesemo s "
"klikom na <guilabel>Namesti</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Download course."
msgstr "Prenesi tečaj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "2. Start Training"
msgstr "2. Začnite z vadbo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Courses consist of multiple training units, each usually grouping a set of "
"phrases according to a scenario. They can be switched by using the combo "
"boxes for language and course at the top boarder of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Tečaji so sestavljeni iz več izobraževalnih enot, od katerih je vsaka "
"običajno združena v niz stavkov glede na scenarij. Preklapljate jih lahko z "
"uporabo kombiniranih polj za jezik in tečaj na zgornjem robu zaslona."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select unit and start training."
msgstr "Izberite enoto in začnite z vadbo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finish Training"
msgstr "Končajte usposabljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "The training can be finished at any point by just closing the program."
msgstr ""
"Usposabljanje lahko kadarkoli zaključite tako, da preprosto zaprete program."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editor"
msgstr "Urednik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The integrated course editor is an advanced tool for language course "
"contributors that allows the creation and collaborative work on language "
"courses for &artikulate;. On the one hand it allows the creation of language "
"courses and recording of the native speaker sound files. On the hand, it "
"enables work on so called <emphasis>skeletons</emphasis>, which are language "
"course prototypes that allow easy and fast creation of new courses derived "
"from a prototype. The editor only edits files outside of the training course "
"set, i.e., the set of courses downloaded in &artikulate;."
msgstr ""
"Integrirani urejevalnik tečajev je napredno orodje za sodelavce jezikovnih "
"tečajev, ki omogoča ustvarjanje in sodelovanje pri jezikovnih tečajih za "
"&artikulate;. Po eni strani omogoča ustvarjanje jezikovnih tečajev in "
"snemanje zvočnih datotek naravnih govorcev. Po drugi strani pa omogoča delo "
"na tako imenovanih <emphasis>skeletonih</emphasis>, ki so prototipi "
"jezikovnih tečajev, ki omogočajo enostavno in hitro ustvarjanje novih "
"tečajev, izpeljanih iz prototipa. Urejevalnik ureja samo datoteke zunaj "
"nabora tečajev usposabljanja, tj. nabora tečajev, prenesenih v &artikulate;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Pregled"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editor Notions"
msgstr "Uredniški pojmi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the course editor we use a specific set of terms, which is also used for "
"the following descriptions."
msgstr ""
"Za urejevalnik predmetov uporabljamo določen niz izrazov, ki se uporablja "
"tudi za naslednje opise."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid "Language:"
msgstr "Jezik:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Languages are only available in &artikulate; if they are given by language "
"specifications."
msgstr ""
"Jeziki so na voljo samo v &artikulate; če so podane z jezikovnimi "
"specifikacijami."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Course:"
msgstr "Tečaj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "A course is associated to one language and contains a list of units."
msgstr "Tečaj je povezan z enim jezikom in vsebuje seznam enot."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unit:"
msgstr "Enota:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A unit consists of phrases that are \"somehow\" homogeneous. E.g. those can "
"be phrases spoken in a restaurant or phrases spoken at a conversation at the "
"street by a tourist searching for the way."
msgstr ""
"Enota je sestavljena iz fraz, ki so \"nekako\" homogene. Npr. to so lahko "
"fraze, izrečene v restavraciji, ali fraze, ki jih v pogovoru na ulici "
"izgovori turist, ki išče pot."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "Course Skeletons:"
msgstr "Tečaj Skeletons:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A course skeleton forms the prototype of a course. This is, skeletons help "
"to ease creation of courses in several languages as they state a set of "
"units and phrases (in English) that then can be used as a blueprint to "
"create a course in a new language. Updates of course skeletons can also be "
"imported into courses that are created from a skeleton."
msgstr ""
"Okostje igrišča tvori prototip igrišča. To pomeni, da okostja pomagajo "
"olajšati ustvarjanje tečajev v več jezikih, saj navajajo niz enot in "
"besednih zvez (v angleščini), ki jih je nato mogoče uporabiti kot načrt za "
"ustvarjanje tečaja v novem jeziku. Posodobitve skeletov tečajev je mogoče "
"uvoziti tudi v tečaje, ki so ustvarjeni iz skeleta."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Phrases:"
msgstr "Fraze:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Phrases are given by a text string and a recording by a native speaker. We "
"differ phrases by their lengths. The following phrase lengths exists"
msgstr ""
"Fraze so podane z besedilnim nizom in posnetkom maternega govorca. Besedne "
"zveze ločimo po dolžini. Obstajajo naslednje dolžine fraz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "word: a single word, letter, or number"
msgstr "beseda: posamezna beseda, črka ali številka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"expression: an expression of several words that does not form a complete "
"sentence"
msgstr "izraz: izraz iz več besed, ki ne tvori celotnega stavka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "sentence: a complete sentence"
msgstr "stavek: popolna poved"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "paragraph: several sentences (usually 2-3)"
msgstr "odstavek: več stavkov (običajno 2-3)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A course is associated with a specific language, consists of different units "
"and each unit is given by a sequence of phrases in different lengths."
msgstr ""
"Tečaj je povezan z določenim jezikom, sestavljen je iz različnih enot in "
"vsaka enota je podana z zaporedjem fraz različnih dolžin."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set Storage Folder/Course Repository"
msgstr "Nastavite mapo za shranjevanje/repozitorij tečajev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor operates within a separate folder (in the following called "
"<emphasis>repository</emphasis>, as it is recommended to be under some "
"version control system). In that folder, the editor searches for editable "
"courses and skeleton files and also stores new files."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik deluje znotraj ločene mape (v nadaljevanju imenovane "
"<emphasis>repozitorij</emphasis>, saj je priporočljivo, da je pod nekaterim "
"sistemom za nadzor različic). V tej mapi urejevalnik išče tečaje in skeletne "
"datoteke, ki jih je mogoče urejati, ter shrani nove datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The course repository can be set in the configuration dialog. It can be "
"found at <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"&artikulate;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and the course settings are at the "
"menu option <guilabel>Course Resources</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Repozitorij tečaja lahko nastavite v konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu. "
"Najdete ga v <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &artikulate;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
"nastavitve tečaja pa so v meniju <guilabel>Viri tečaja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Set course repository for editor.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nastavi repozitorij tečaja za urejevalnik.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Set course repository for editor.</para>"
msgstr "<para>Nastavi repozitorij tečaja za urejevalnik.</para>"

